e verbunden sind, die keinesfalls zu einer allmählichen Auflösung dieser Zimmer führt.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aCall centers. 0aControl rooms. 4aArbeit. 4aArchitektur. 4aDigitalisierung. 4aInfrastruktur. 4aKontrolle. 4aModerne. 4aRefiguration. 4aSmart City. 4aSoziologie. 4aSteuerung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aArchitecture.  aControl System.  aControl.  aDigitalization.  aInfrastructure.  aModernity.  aRefiguration.  aSmart City.  aSociology.  aWork.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2022z9783110994520oZDB-23-DSL08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2022z9783111025094oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839462331?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839462331zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839462331/original  a978-3-11-076700-1 DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSLb2022  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-TGPb2022